"title": "8454: obedience, to God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8454: obedience, to god",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A willingness to submit oneself to the will of God and to put it into effect. Scripture emphasises the necessity for God's laws to be followed, gives examples and reasons, and describes the rewards.</p>\n<h2>Obedience is demanded of God's people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:18\">LEV 25:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:22\">1SA 15:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:16\">DEU 26:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:46\">DEU 32:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:16-Rom6:18\">ROM 6:16–6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:14-1Pet1:16\">1PE 1:14–1:16</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of obedience in the OT</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:15\">JOS 11:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:22\">GEN 6:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:1-Gen12:4\">GEN 12:1–12:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:2-Gen22:3\">GEN 22:2–22:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:16\">EXO 40:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:3\">JON 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>The example of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:39\">MAT 26:39</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:36\">MRK 14:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:42\">LUK 22:42</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:31\">JHN 14:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:4\">JHN 17:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:19\">ROM 5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:8\">PHP 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:8\">HEB 5:8</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is obeyed</h2>\n<h3>By the wind and the waves</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:26-Matt8:27\">MAT 8:26–8:27</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:39-Mark4:41\">MRK 4:39–4:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:24-Luke8:25\">LUK 8:24–8:25</a></p>\n<h3>By evil spirits</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:27\">MRK 1:27</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:36\">LUK 4:36</a></p>\n<h2>Obedience and love</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:15\">JHN 14:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:3\">1JN 5:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:167\">PSA 119:167</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:5\">1JN 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:10\">1JN 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:6\">2JN 1:6</a></p>\n<h2>Obedience and faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:8\">HEB 11:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:21\">MAT 7:21</a></strong> <em>Obedience to the will of God demonstrates the reality of a person's faith in Jesus Christ.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:5\">ROM 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:14-Jas2:26\">JAS 2:14–2:26</a></p>\n<h2>God rewards those who obey him</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:5\">EXO 19:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:10\">JHN 15:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:29\">DEU 5:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:14\">1KI 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:5-2Kgs18:7\">2KI 18:5–18:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:21\">MAT 7:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24-Matt7:25\">MAT 7:24–7:25</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:47-Luke6:48\">LUK 6:47–6:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:50\">MAT 12:50</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:35\">MRK 3:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:21\">LUK 8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:26\">JHN 12:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:21\">JHN 14:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:23\">JHN 14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:4-John21:6\">JHN 21:4–21:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:17\">1JN 2:17</a></p>\n<h2>Obedience to the word of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24-Matt7:27\">MAT 7:24–7:27</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:22\">JAS 1:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:9-Ps119:11\">PSA 119:9–119:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:3\">JON 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:28\">LUK 11:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:6\">JHN 17:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:14-Jas2:20\">JAS 2:14–2:20</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of people who obeyed God</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:9\">GEN 6:9</a> <em>Noah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:1-Gen12:4\">GEN 12:1–12:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:23\">GEN 17:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:30\">PSA 119:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:100-Ps119:106\">PSA 119:100–119:106</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:19-Acts4:20\">ACT 4:19–4:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:29\">ACT 5:29</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:7-Phil3:14\">PHP 3:7–3:14</a> <em>Paul</em></p>",
